===========================
Changing Difficulty In-Game
===========================

  *** IMPORTANT ***
  The ingame difficulty adjustment has no affect on MHM (unless you are using particular subsets of modules).
  Difficulty is controlled by MHM and the options you choose to install.
  See below for ways to change.

=======================================
Changing Difficulty Via Installed Files
=======================================

You can change the difficulty of MHM during a playthrough by changing the installed files.

Exception: Once you have campfire saves in your game (addon: 'Campfire Saves', or addon: 'Master Mode'), you need to keep it for that playthrough.
           You can swap Master-Mode for Campfires, but that's it.

See chart below about what difficulty you can change to from a particular initial stage.



CHANGE FROM                CHANGE TO                         HOW

Standard                   --> Standard+Campfires            Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak"
Standard                   --> Standard+Relaxed              Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"
Standard                   --> Standard+Relaxed+Campfires    Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak".
Standard                   --> Hardcore                      Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak"
Standard                   --> Hardcore+Campfires            Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak"
Standard                   --> Hardcore+MasterMode           Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzzz_Master_Mode_Hardcore_AIO_P.pak"


CHANGE FROM                CHANGE TO                         HOW

Standard+Campfires         --> Standard                      Too bad
Standard+Campfires         --> Standard+Relaxed              Too bad
Standard+Campfires         --> Standard+Relaxed+Campfires    Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"
Standard+Campfires         --> Hardcore                      Too bad
Standard+Campfires         --> Hardcore+Campfires            Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak"
Standard+Campfires         --> Hardcore+MasterMode           Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzzz_Master_Mode_Hardcore_AIO_P.pak". Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak"


CHANGE FROM                CHANGE TO                         HOW

Standard+Relaxed           --> Standard                      Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"
Standard+Relaxed           --> Standard+Campfires            Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak"
Standard+Relaxed           --> Standard+Relaxed+Campfires    Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak"
Standard+Relaxed           --> Hardcore                       Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak". Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak".
Standard+Relaxed           --> Hardcore+Campfires            Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak". Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"
Standard+Relaxed           --> Hardcore+MasterMode           Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzzz_Master_Mode_Hardcore_AIO_P.pak". Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"


CHANGE FROM                CHANGE TO                         HOW

Standard+Relaxed+Campfires --> Standard                      Too bad
Standard+Relaxed+Campfires --> Standard+Campfires            Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"
Standard+Relaxed+Campfires --> Standard+Relaxed              Too bad
Standard+Relaxed+Campfires --> Hardcore                      Too bad
Standard+Relaxed+Campfires --> Hardcore+Campfires            Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak". Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"
Standard+Relaxed+Campfires --> Hardcore+MasterMode           Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak". Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak". Remove "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzzz_Master_Mode_Hardcore_AIO_P.pak"


