Hardcore                   --> Standard                      Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak"
Hardcore                   --> Standard+Campfires            Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak"		
Hardcore                   --> Standard+Relaxed              Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"
Hardcore                   --> Standard+Relaxed+Campfires    Replace "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Hardcore.pak" with "zzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_AIO_Full_Standard.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak". Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_2.0_Relaxed_Mode_Veteran_AIO_P.pak"
Hardcore                   --> Hardcore+Campfires            Add "zzzzzzzzzzzz_MHM_CampfireSaves.pak"
Hardcore                   --> Hardcore+MasterMode           Add "zzzzzzzzzzzzz_Master_Mode_Hardcore_AIO_P.pak"


